54hqs4AD0Q7kNvgG2Mu90&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAaQk3h5R_iQvaxMJPKRbHpRfWfDsNN1h1C7fKfO0ubvg&oe=66FBF7FC"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverArt_Landscape.png", "id": "820035533223852", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982447_820035536557185_289606171667312693_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UDMTUClFnXUQ7kNvgEc4IF5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAj8Igc35kY32SbahNgUN121qsZKADmWk2NPpONohGJJQ&oe=66FBF26D"}, "display_name": "VAIL", "keywords": ["shooter", "fps", "multiplayer", "gun", "social"], "long_description": "Immerse yourself in the world of VAIL, a multiplayer FPS game built for virtual reality. Engage in high-octane gameplay centered around objective-based game modes or connect with a vibrant community in social environments. Set in a sci-fi future of the solar system, choose between opposing factions and battle for the claim to humanity\u2019s legacy.\n{390905377282488}\n\n#  **EXPERIENCE UNPARALLELED COMBAT**\n\nFeel high-impact FPS combat with best-in-class shooter mechanics, precisely tuned interactions, and immersive physics systems.\n\n{1162628724924512}\n\n# **LEVEL UP AND UNLOCK REWARDS**\n\nDominate in popular team-based and free-for-all game modes as you level up, unlock rewards, and top the leaderboards.\n\n{766149719046755}\n\n#  **UNCOVER VAIL'S STORY**\nTraverse through awe-inspiring brutalist environments as the lines between right and wrong begin to blur.\n\n\n{1884336785321853}\n\n# **YOUR NEXT BEST FRIEND IS ONE REALITY AWAY**\n\nUnite with your friends for battle, or bring them to your Armory to play mini-games and chill.\n\n{1136583027611274}\n\n# **CRITICALLY ACCLAIMED**\n\n\n{481558107552824}", "short_description": "Immerse yourself in the unparalleled world of VAIL, a hybrid first-person shooter game built for virtual reality. Engage in high-octane gameplay centered around objective-based game modes or connect with a vibrant community in social 